# adapters.reg — ADAPTER REGISTRY. The BIOS scans this file; adapters are NOT
# hardcoded in the BIOS. As new adapters are built, register one line here.
# format:  name : kind : source : description
# kind: ingress (feeds the wire bus) | display (off-fabric monitor)
xau_backtest : ingress : adapter/data_synth.bin   : XAU synthetic backtest feed
xau_live     : ingress : adapter/data_xau_test.csv : XAU live test tick data
monitor      : display : display/display_adapter.h : off-fabric display adapter (TUI)
